Preconditions:
- The input grid must not be null.
- The input grid must have at least one row and one column.

Postconditions:
- The returned matrix `answer` must have the same number of rows as the input grid.
- The returned matrix `answer` must have the same number of columns as the input grid.
- The values in the returned matrix `answer` must be integers.
- The values in the returned matrix `answer` must represent the difference between the distinct values in the corresponding positions of the input grid.